Title: Silverlight Web Comic
Description:
http://webcomic.freeiz.com/ Makes easier for the people create your own comic with your own pictures o drawings, and add the globes of text like the comics on a predefined frames.
It's developed in silverlight 4 with vb .net and on the future a sql database for save the comics.
